{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act19side_level_act19side_06_end","storyGroup":"act19side","storySort":14,"storyDependence":"act19side_level_act19side_06_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"DV-6","storyName":"挣脱美梦","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"拓荒者们与多萝西达成和解，多萝西也答应暂停实验，局势似乎正在好转，斐尔迪南却决定孤注一掷，让工作人员给拓荒者们注射递质。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act19side/level_act19side_06_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act19side_06","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":12,"next":14,"characters":["白面鸮","桑尼","赫默","埃琳娜","多萝西","帕尔维斯","斐尔迪南","莱茵防卫科成员","上校的声音","拓荒队成员"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"Dialog","id":1},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":2},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":3},{"type":"Background","image":"29_g5_laboratory","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":5},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$dignified_intro","key":"$dignified_loop","volume":"0.6","crossfade":"1","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":7},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"......桑尼。","id":8},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":9},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"我们是自愿的。","id":10},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#1$1","id":11},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"摩尔医生，我不明白......您是在代表谁发言？","id":12},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#8$1","id":13},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"......","id":14},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":15},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"信息。","id":16},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":17},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"我接收到了信息，不同于过去的信息。","id":18},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#8$1","id":19},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"唔......","id":20},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#6$1","id":21},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"乔伊丝，是不是头又疼了？","id":22},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":23},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"我的身体没有问题，赫默医生。","id":24},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":25},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"一些未经允许的数据涌入了系统中枢。需要额外处理。","id":26},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#7$1","id":27},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"......数据？","id":28},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":29},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"嗯......桑尼，我们都知道......","id":30},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":31},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"这是一场......冒险。","id":32},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":33},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"结果......难以预料，但这是我们的选择。","id":34},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":35},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"数据传输中断，系统判断以上信息的接收者应为桑尼先生。","id":36},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#7$1","id":37},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"摩尔医生，您说话的语气就好像您是我们......不，躺在那里的受试者之中的一员一样。","id":38},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":39},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"无法确认上述假设。","id":40},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":41},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"数据来源未知，我只是感受到了它们。","id":42},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#7$1","id":43},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"这是真的吗，赫默医生？摩尔医生能听到我们的同伴们的声音？！","id":44},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":45},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......乔伊丝，你选择了感受这个词语？","id":46},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":47},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"是的，赫默医生。","id":48},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":49},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"梦境的内容发生了变化。","id":50},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":51},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"你看到了什么？","id":52},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":53},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"无法解析。","id":54},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#3$1","id":55},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"你的眼神和平时差别好大......你是感受到悲伤了吗？","id":56},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":57},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"检测到边缘系统信号强烈波动。","id":58},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":59},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"......戴拉。","id":60},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#5$1","id":61},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"戴拉蕾德？你又想起了她......难道九号装置和弗兰克斯主任的实验也有联系？","id":62},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":63},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"动机，情感，而非逻辑联系。","id":64},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":65},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"赫默医生，我能感受到，这是我们的选择。","id":66},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":67},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"你们的......选择？","id":68},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":69},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......","id":70},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#7$1","id":71},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"桑尼先生，假如我向你保证，我会尽一切努力让所有错误都得到纠正，你是否愿意暂时放过多萝西·弗兰克斯？","id":72},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#1$1","id":73},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"......赫默医生，我们感激您一路上的帮助，更感激您为我们揭示了实验的真相。","id":74},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#1$1","id":75},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"我愿意相信您会站在我们这边——","id":76},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":77},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"但您真的能保证这个人不会重启实验吗？","id":78},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1","id":79},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"......","id":80},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#7$1","id":81},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我不能。","id":82},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#7$1","id":83},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"可万一她真的这么做了，我会替你解决她。","id":84},{"type":"Dialog","id":85},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":86},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":87},{"type":"Background","image":"29_g4_corridor","screenadapt":"coverall","id":88},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":89},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#11$1","id":90},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"呼......实验暂停，多萝西没有受伤，受试者们也正在逐渐恢复意识......","id":91},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#11$1","id":92},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"我还有些不敢相信。","id":93},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":94},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"请不必担心，情绪起伏是正常现象。","id":95},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#11$1","id":96},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"乔伊丝，你醒得太及时了。","id":97},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1","id":98},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"我从来没见过奥利维亚那么生气......我真怕她会不管多萝西。","id":99},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1","id":100},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"但我还是搞不明白，你为什么能听到受试者们的声音......","id":101},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1","id":102},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"他们的意识是被多萝西的“中枢”连在一起的，可你明明在外面，你到底是怎么被卷进去的？","id":103},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1","id":104},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"你不是说，九号装置与“中枢”无关吗？","id":105},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":106},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"有效信息不足，无法做出判断。","id":107},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":108},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"但是，在梦醒的时候，我听到了迈尔先生的声音。","id":109},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#3$1","id":110},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"梦醒的时候......","id":111},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#3$1","id":112},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"那场发生在走廊上的冲突？就连之前的战斗都没能起到作用，为什么那会唤醒你？","id":113},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#3$1","id":114},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"好奇怪......","id":115},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#10$1","id":116},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"不过事情解决了就好，多亏了奥利维亚。","id":117},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":118},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"赫默医生做到了，符合预期。","id":119},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#11$1","id":120},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"现在想想......她变化真大啊。","id":121},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#11$1","id":122},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"我刚认识她的时候，她还是个......唔，就大学里很常见的那种好学生，文静腼腆，不太爱说话。","id":123},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":124},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"以上描述与我的记忆相符。","id":125},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#11$1","id":126},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"刚刚她逼问多萝西又力保多萝西的时候，我都快认不出她来了。","id":127},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#11$1","id":128},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"就仿佛看到了......另一个人的影子。","id":129},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":130},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"乌比卡研究员，你联想的对象是否是塞雷娅主任？","id":131},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1","id":132},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"你、你怎么说出来了？","id":133},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1","id":134},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"你可别告诉奥利维亚我说了这样的话啊！","id":135},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":136},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"赫默医生并不会因此质疑你与她之间的友谊。","id":137},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#11$1","id":138},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"......我知道。","id":139},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#11$1","id":140},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"只是作为她的朋友，我也不想让她在这么麻烦的时刻想起不太愉快的往事。","id":141},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":142},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"理解。","id":143},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#11$1","id":144},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"走吧，我也该继续完成工作了。","id":145},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#11$1","id":146},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"通讯......通讯还没有恢复吗？糟了，老板那边......","id":147},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1","id":148},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"还有姐姐，真不知道她会给我发多少消息......","id":149},{"type":"Dialog","id":150},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":151},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":152},{"type":"Background","image":"29_g5_laboratory","screenadapt":"coverall","id":153},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":154},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#7$1","id":155},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"弗兰克斯主任，麻烦你跟我一起离开实验区。","id":156},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1","id":157},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"......请等一下。","id":158},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1","id":159},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"既然实验停了，他们一定不会让这间实验室留下。","id":160},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1","id":161},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"有一样东西......我必须带走。","id":162},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#7$1","id":163},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"这是......照片？","id":164},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1","id":165},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"嗯。","id":166},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":167},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"照片上这些都是拓荒者......","id":168},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":169},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"这孩子是......你？","id":170},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1","id":171},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"......赫默医生，我对桑尼说的话，都是真心的。","id":172},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1","id":173},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"我的母亲，我所有的亲人......曾经都是拓荒者。","id":174},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"我从小就听他们诉说自己的梦想，见过他们的奋斗，也目睹过他们的挣扎。","id":175},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"是他们的付出令我有机会去追逐我自己的梦想。","id":176},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"可是我所拥有的幸运......大多数拓荒者都不可能拥有。","id":177},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":178},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"你的家人们，他们现在......","id":179},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1","id":180},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"......他们之中的大多数都已经离开了我。","id":181},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"就在我得到铸铁城理工大学的邀请，回城参加他们为极少数所谓“天才”举办的夏令营的时候......","id":182},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"一场天灾摧毁了我母亲所在的临时基地。","id":183},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"成为一名研究者......曾经也是她的梦想。可她再也没能等到我得到奖学金，被破格录取的好消息。","id":184},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#6$1","id":185},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"你一定非常难过......","id":186},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1","id":187},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"赫默医生，停下这个实验，真的是正确的选择吗？","id":188},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1","id":189},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"那些拓荒者，那些被生活逼得走投无路的人们，他们或许明天就会遭遇厄运。","id":190},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1","id":191},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"而我本可以救他们......","id":192},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1","id":193},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"多萝西","text":"他们不必像我的亲人们一样，绝望地被沙暴吞噬。","id":194},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":195},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......","id":196},{"type":"Dialog","id":197},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":198},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":199},{"type":"Background","image":"29_g4_corridor","screenadapt":"coverall","id":200},{"type":"cameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"1","fadetime":"0","id":201},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":202},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","id":203},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"赫默，为什么要问我这样的问题？","id":204},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","id":205},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"没有我们的实验，那个孩子在离开海顿一号实验室之后根本活不了几天。","id":206},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","id":207},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"我们救活了她，我甚至让你照顾她的起居，她不仅能享受衣食无忧的生活，还能为推动科学进步做贡献——","id":208},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","id":209},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"相比在荒野上因为矿石病而悄无声息死去的孩子们，她是多么幸运啊。","id":210},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_531_1#1$1","id":211},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕尔维斯","text":"我那么信任你、器重你，你竟然......在这么细枝末节的操作问题上指责我、指责科学本身？","id":212},{"type":"Dialog","id":213},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":214},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":215},{"type":"Background","image":"29_g5_laboratory","screenadapt":"coverall","id":216},{"type":"cameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0","fadetime":"0","id":217},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":218},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#6$1","id":219},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......我不知道。","id":220},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#6$1","id":221},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"这个答案也不应该由我告诉你。","id":222},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":223},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"乔伊丝提醒了我——","id":224},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":225},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"即便我永远不会赞同你们......你的行为，我也不该用我的标准来评判一切。","id":226},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#10$1","id":227},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"被自我怀疑与不确定性折磨，难道不正是我们选择的命运？","id":228},{"type":"character","name":"avg_108_silent_1#7$1","id":229},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"身为研究者，我们只能自己去找答案。","id":230},{"type":"Dialog","id":231},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":232},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":233},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":234},{"type":"Background","image":"29_g11_monitoringroom","screenadapt":"coverall","id":235},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":236},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","fadetime":"1","id":237},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":238},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"$darkness01_loop","volume":"0.6","crossfade":"1","id":239,"musicid":1},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"都布置好了吗？","id":240},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":241},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"我们的人已经进入基地，正在靠近实验区。","id":242},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","id":243},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"好，做好准备。","id":244},{"type":"Dialog","id":245},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","volume":"0.9","id":246},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":247},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":248},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"上校先生，我明白现在已经有些迟了，请再给我一些时间......","id":249},{"type":"character","id":250},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"上校的声音","text":"......克鲁尼，你没有告诉我，有其他人进入了基地。","id":251},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":252},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"您是指......那家医药企业？","id":253},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#1$1","id":254},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"您不必担心，他们是莱茵生命的合作方，我一定......","id":255},{"type":"character","id":256},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"上校的声音","text":"你的保证没有意义。","id":257},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"上校的声音","text":"结果——我们要的只有结果。","id":258},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#5$1","id":259},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"我很抱歉，只是一点小小的延迟......","id":260},{"type":"character","id":261},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"上校的声音","text":"没有结果的话，至少别给我们惹麻烦。","id":262},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"上校的声音","text":"记住这句话。","id":263},{"type":"Dialog","id":264},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$transmission","volume":"0.9","id":265},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":266},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","id":267},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"......","id":268},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":269},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"还要继续行动吗，斐尔迪南主任？","id":270},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","id":271},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"......我并不认为眼前还有其他选择。","id":272},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":273},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"明白了。","id":274},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","id":275},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"对了......","id":276},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","id":277},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"替我接通特殊通讯频道。","id":278},{"type":"Dialog","id":279},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":280},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":281},{"type":"Background","image":"29_g4_corridor","screenadapt":"coverall","id":282},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":283},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#7$1","id":284},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"咦......通讯？突然通了？","id":285},{"type":"Dialog","id":286},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","volume":"0.9","id":287},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":288},{"type":"character","id":289},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"......埃琳娜。","id":290},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#7$1","id":291},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"主任？","id":292},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#10$1","id":293},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"太好了，我一直都想联系您，可惜连不上......您收到我的信息了吗？我把基地里发生的事情都写进了简报里。","id":294},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#11$1","id":295},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"多萝西......弗兰克斯主任的实验出了点岔子，不过没关系，我和赫默研究员处理好了。","id":296},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#11$1","id":297},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"还有拓荒者，他们也被安抚好了，正在离开实验区......","id":298},{"type":"character","id":299},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"......我知道。","id":300},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#7$1","id":301},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"您......您知道？这么快......不愧是您。","id":302},{"type":"character","id":303},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"你做到了你该做的事，接下来会由其他人过来清理现场。","id":304},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#7$1","id":305},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"您是说防卫科的同事们？他们终于进来了吗？","id":306},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#10$1","id":307},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"呼......那我更放心了。我还在担心实验区储存的那些递质......","id":308},{"type":"character","id":309},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"他们知道该怎么做，你可以撤出来了。","id":310},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#11$1","id":311},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"主任，我还是留下帮他们吧，除了多萝西，基地里只有我对实验内容最熟悉。","id":312},{"type":"character","id":313},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"埃琳娜，我此刻就在监控站，难道两位主任还控制不了局面？","id":314},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1","id":315},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"我不是这个意思......","id":316},{"type":"character","id":317},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"那就听我的话，立刻撤出实验基地。","id":318},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#8$1","id":319},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"我能问一下为什么吗？","id":320},{"type":"character","id":321},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"别用这些没有意义的提问浪费我的时间。马上来监控室见我。","id":322},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1","id":323},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"......是，主任。","id":324},{"type":"Dialog","id":325},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$transmission","volume":"0.9","id":326},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":327},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#11$1","id":328},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"......","id":329},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":330},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"有什么问题吗，乌比卡研究员？","id":331},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#12$1","id":332},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"主任......斐尔迪南让我立刻撤离。","id":333},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":334},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"撤离？","id":335},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#9$1","id":336},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"乔伊丝，你先去通知奥利维亚吧，防卫科的人就要到了。","id":337},{"type":"character","name":"avg_128_plosis_1#1$1","id":338},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"白面鸮","text":"那你呢，要离开这里吗？","id":339},{"type":"character","name":"avg_135_halo_1#3$1","id":340},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"埃琳娜","text":"我......主任的反应不太对劲。如果说......他并不知道多萝西走到了哪一步，那他为什么对实验出的状况毫不关心？","id":341},{"type":"Dialog","id":342},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":343},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":344},{"type":"Background","image":"29_g11_monitoringroom","screenadapt":"coverall","id":345},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":346},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":347},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"斐尔迪南主任，埃琳娜小姐并未离开实验区。","id":348},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","id":349},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"......","id":350},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":351},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"是否中断计划？","id":352},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","id":353},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"......不用。","id":354},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_522_1#6$1","id":355},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斐尔迪南","text":"我们继续。","id":356},{"type":"Dialog","id":357},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":358},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":359},{"type":"Background","image":"29_g4_corridor","screenadapt":"coverall","id":360},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":361},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":362},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"其他人都撤出去了吗？","id":363},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","id":364},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"是的，领队。","id":365},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":366},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"下一个。","id":367},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#7$1","id":368},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"他们在做什么？","id":369},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","id":370},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"说是什么预防程序，大概是想给我们打什么镇定剂吧。","id":371},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","id":372},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"我们也算是闹了很大一通，是吧，头儿？","id":373},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#1$1","id":374},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"......别忘了我说过的，等他们问起来，事情都是我做的。","id":375},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_534_1#1$1","id":376},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拓荒队成员","text":"放心吧，不会让你一个人担着的。","id":377},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#2$1","id":378},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"你这家伙......","id":379},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":380},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"下一个。","id":381},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":382},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"......我叫桑尼·罗马诺。","id":383},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":384},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"我没问你姓名。","id":385},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#1$1","id":386},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"麻烦你跟你们头领说一声，绑架的事情都是我的个人行为。","id":387},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":388},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"......","id":389},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_528_1#1$1","id":390},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱茵防卫科成员","text":"右手。","id":391},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_535_1#11$1","id":392},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"桑尼","text":"打完针以后，你们总该处理这件事了吧？","id":393},{"type":"dialog","id":394},{"type":"Character","na